Comment: 5,0:12:56.63,0:12:57.78,Alt,sub 1,0,0,0,,Hayama-chan...
Comment: 5,0:13:52.98,0:13:54.63,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,How can you make Yoko-sama shovel snow?!
Comment: 5,0:13:55.83,0:13:58.18,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Sonobe-san, you must have made it snow!
Comment: 5,0:14:23.88,0:14:24.83,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Futaba-san!
