Comment: 5,0:16:46.01,0:16:49.38,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,That is, of course, if Hayama-san\Nand Futaba-san agree to it.
Comment: 5,0:19:10.03,0:19:11.38,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,Yoko-sama!
Comment: 5,0:19:25.28,0:19:27.50,Default,sub 1,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do, Sonobe-san?
