Dialogue: 5,0:00:51.98,0:00:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the day to gorge on chicken and cake!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:54.73,0:00:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're acting strange...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:56.08,0:00:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:56.68,0:00:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...the both of you.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:02.43,0:01:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat paws are amazing!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:43.93,0:01:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy, that's a pretty Christmas tree!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:45.55,0:01:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:47.35,0:01:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally the season, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:50.35,0:01:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:53.04,0:01:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The season for my heating bill to be costly.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:55.53,0:01:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't what I meant...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:57.98,0:02:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It has gotten pretty cold.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:00.38,0:02:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get out of bed this morning.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:02.75,0:02:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:04.07,0:02:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:05.23,0:02:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can just wrap myself\Nin blankets when I am home.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:08.73,0:02:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I can save on heating!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:11.33,0:02:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:14.73,0:02:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:16.03,0:02:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I will buy a heater for you!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.28,0:02:19.28,Alt,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:20.43,0:02:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, apologies.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:21.58,0:02:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.78,0:02:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I wanted to say that\Nthe {\i1}Christmas{\i0} season is here!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:30.44,0:02:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.37,0:02:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Christmas is an important day!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:34.96,0:02:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the day to gorge on chicken and cake!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:38.13,0:02:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what Christmas is for.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:40.15,0:02:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:40.88,0:02:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what else is it for, here in Japan?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:44.83,0:02:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it {\i1}has{\i0} become a day\Nfor chicken and cake here.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:47.94,0:02:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's have a party!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:50.08,0:02:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A party!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.08,0:02:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My, what a wonderful idea.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:53.49,0:02:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.70,0:02:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll gorge on chicken and cake!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.60,0:03:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, that is not what Christmas is for...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:02.21,0:03:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm excited for the party.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.02,0:03:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:15.12,0:03:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, she had some class rep duties.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.69,0:03:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She sounds busy.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:20.40,0:03:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a good student.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.48,0:03:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She's great at looking good\Nin front of teachers, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:23.18,0:03:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, about the Christmas party,\NI'll be baking the cake, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:27.32,0:03:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My, how fantastic!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.57,0:03:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you talking about\NChristmas plans just now?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.83,0:03:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the three of us are having a party.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.20,0:03:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you something you might want to know.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.88,0:03:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.88,0:03:50.80,Alt,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.80,0:03:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Christmas also happens to be...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.18,0:03:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...birthday!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.13,0:04:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.13,0:04:00.90,Alt,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.28,0:04:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:18.66,0:04:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with you two?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.10,0:04:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.38,0:04:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.48,0:04:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A devil was born on a holy night?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.87,0:04:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Such contradictory occurrences!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.43,0:04:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine if you're a fallen angel— I mean,\Nit doesn't matter when you were born!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite right!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.53,0:04:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All planned by God— I mean, the Devil?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:00.92,0:05:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you both talking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.18,0:05:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're acting strange...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:06.64,0:05:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:06.64,0:05:07.13,Alt,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:07.13,0:05:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...the both of you.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:09.25,0:05:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.46,0:05:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say...{said no such thing}.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.27,0:05:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:22.60,0:05:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm nervous, because I'm\Nthinking about it too much.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:24.99,0:05:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed{Me, too}.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.48,0:05:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do on Christmas?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.68,0:05:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.27,0:05:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.68,0:05:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's surprise her by telling her it's a Christmas\Nparty, but it'll actually be her birthday party.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.49,0:05:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.58,0:05:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We will set up a trap for her!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.77,0:05:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not supposed to be a trap...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.85,0:05:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.07,0:05:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Sonobe?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.31,0:06:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Passing out Christmas cake flyers.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.73,0:06:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you before to stop\Npassing out flyers here.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.93,0:06:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.08,0:06:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that if our sales go up,\NI might give you a raise...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.83,0:06:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.03,0:06:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:14.33,0:06:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home, this instant!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.58,0:06:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Cake shops must be busy\Nat this time of year.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.78,0:06:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.28,0:06:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We have cake orders and\Nhave started making stollen.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:25.58,0:06:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am helping too{I have been helping}.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.96,0:06:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making cakes, too?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.88,0:06:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I help out measuring and\Nsprinkling things on top.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:33.58,0:06:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it takes longer with more people,\Nbut it's helpful at this time of year.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:38.83,0:06:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course{ I am helpful}!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.80,0:06:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.58,0:06:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what's with this conversation...?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:47.93,0:06:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, does that mean you'll\Nbe working on Christmas?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:53.28,0:06:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I give you permission\Nto take that day off!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.88,0:06:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.88,0:06:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You have finally made friends.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.43,0:07:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of your friend's birthday party,\NI am willing to work my fingers to the bone!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.93,0:07:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonobe...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:05.88,0:07:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, frankly, her usefulness level is more than a cat's paw.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.48,0:07:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course{ I am}!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.53,0:07:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, really, what's with this conversation?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.05,0:07:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.58,0:07:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cat paws are amazing!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.58,0:07:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why—
Dialogue: 5,0:07:21.77,0:07:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Because obviously I'm curious about\Nwhat do you two want to talk{have to say that I can't hear}.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.08,0:07:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, we have been hiding\Nsomething from you.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonobe!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.54,0:07:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.03,0:07:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm planning on making\Nbear and cat-shaped cakes.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.13,0:07:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.13,0:07:38.19,Alt,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:38.19,0:07:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:40.78,0:07:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept it a secret, because\NI wanted to surprise you.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.20,0:07:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you can keep as many of those\Nkinds of secrets as you want!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.38,0:07:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're off the hook, somehow.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.26,0:07:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonobe got us out of this one.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.13,0:08:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I love Christmas.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.48,0:08:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The streets are buzzing with excitement.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.03,0:08:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's fun to pick out presents.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.03,0:08:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one is better?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Pink?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.83,0:08:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The red one's good, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:19.58,0:08:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It took an hour to decide,\Nand I ended up getting both.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.30,0:08:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I splurged and invested all\Nof this month's allowance.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:27.07,0:08:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's the plan for that day.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:29.71,0:08:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the first time I am throwing\Na birthday party for a friend.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.08,0:08:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's have a great Christmas!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.58,0:08:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.47,0:08:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:43.60,0:08:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.99,0:08:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it about Hayama's birthday?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:47.58,0:08:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you overheard?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.78,0:08:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:53.48,0:08:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're having a surprise birthday\Nparty for her, so keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.23,0:08:58.83,Alt,,0,0,0,,I'll buy something for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.23,0:08:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:58.83,0:09:03.28,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yay! I've been wanting the premium card game!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:01.48,0:09:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.53,0:09:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...{I-I can't believe it.}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.28,0:09:04.08,Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm excited.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.08,0:09:04.68,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:11.88,0:09:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.29,0:09:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishiyama?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.24,0:09:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nishiyama?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.73,0:09:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Christmas...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:19.23,0:09:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Christmas is...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:21.83,0:09:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you {\i1}do{\i0} like Christmas.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.78,0:09:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This year—
Dialogue: 5,0:09:25.13,0:09:26.28,Alt,,0,0,0,,I don't care...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.28,0:09:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.58,0:09:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to celebrate, anyway.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.08,0:09:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.69,0:09:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:32.26,0:09:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}love{\i0} Christmas.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.09,0:09:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a Christmas party.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:37.03,0:09:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.43,0:09:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll just eat curry on Christmas.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:44.08,0:09:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:45.21,0:09:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're having a Christmas party with me!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:48.63,0:09:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, get up!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:50.58,0:09:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go buy a cake!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.64,0:10:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring this with you.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.83,0:10:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Have fun at the party.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, where should I put this?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:44.85,0:10:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.63,0:10:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's here!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.63,0:10:50.48,Alt,,0,0,0,,She's here!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.86,0:10:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.98,0:10:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy Birthda—
Dialogue: 5,0:10:58.58,0:11:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you scared me!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:00.48,0:11:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were going to shoot me!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:02.93,0:11:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot you?!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.93,0:11:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside, you had a very\N{ pretty intense expression on your} amazing face just now!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.24,0:11:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want you to feel like you had to\Ncelebrate with me, so I didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.31,0:11:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why{Is that why you didn't tell us?}...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:19.48,0:11:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I usually celebrate along with Christmas anyway,\Nso I'm used to my birthday being secondary.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so sad.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.88,0:11:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:29.31,0:11:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been years since I've\Ncelebrated with friends.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.03,0:11:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's have some cake.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:37.03,0:11:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.28,0:11:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I helped, too!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.28,0:11:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I measured and sprinkled things on top.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.53,0:11:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, I have something, too...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I will eat it!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:54.78,0:11:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.68,0:11:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't force yourself.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.33,0:12:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:12.43,0:12:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I feel like I could run\Na whole marathon.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.13,0:12:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It was no good{Maybe she shouldn't have eaten it}, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.23,0:12:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected{Ugh}.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.08,0:12:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, now.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:33.83,0:12:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand that Christmas\Nwas also Hayama's birthday.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.38,0:12:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you able to enjoy your Christmas?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.88,0:12:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayama?!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:44.73,0:12:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was also the day I was\Nbrought into this world!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:47.73,0:12:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologize!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.87,0:12:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologize to Christmas!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, what for?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.79,0:12:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The streets celebrate my advent.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologize!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:57.28,0:12:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just, apologize!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:00.13,0:13:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologize to Christmas!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.48,0:13:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first snow of the winter...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:28.17,0:13:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it's piled up so much.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.03,0:13:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Unusual weather.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:35.19,0:13:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But the snow is really exhilarating.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot open unless we\Nclear this snow away, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.73,0:13:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:48.11,0:13:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How cold!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.20,0:13:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My back aches, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.38,0:13:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.98,0:13:55.83,Alt,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho, heave-ho.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.73,0:14:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the first to accuse me of that.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:03.73,0:14:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It is still snowing.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.39,0:14:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.89,0:14:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking, will the snow\Nstop people from coming?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.28,0:14:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Not necessarily.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.18,0:14:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Blizzards and typhoons exhilarate people and make them want to go out.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:17.93,0:14:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what happens?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:21.13,0:14:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have some!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.05,0:14:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:24.83,0:14:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You are having cake on\Na snowy day like today?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:26.99,0:14:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, somehow, when I saw the snow, it gave me a craving for cake.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:31.41,0:14:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, one with white whipped cream?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:34.93,0:14:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tiramisu, chocolate ganache,\Nand opera cake, please!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.08,0:14:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Has the snow around you melted?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's snowing a lot!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.27,0:14:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go out!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.17,0:14:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:49.22,0:14:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.83,0:14:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a nice blanket of snow.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.93,0:14:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a waste not to go out!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:54.93,0:14:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying warm indoors\Nis the best on cold days.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.13,0:15:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:00.73,0:15:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for a little.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:01.98,0:15:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really cool!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.28,0:15:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah, hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.38,0:15:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.13,0:15:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a snow hut!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.13,0:15:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You made this by yourself?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.58,0:15:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know it's possible to make one!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.73,0:15:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.13,0:15:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's warm inside.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:19.68,0:15:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, go inside.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.33,0:15:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring something to drink.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.53,0:15:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We can drink it inside.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.98,0:15:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is warm in here.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.18,0:15:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How strange.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's made out of cold snow{, but it's warm}...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:49.83,0:15:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In the garden?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:57.78,0:16:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I should've stayed in.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:10.38,0:16:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:11.95,0:16:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I got an email saying that you're in trouble.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:16.98,0:16:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...use the doorbell.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.51,0:16:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The snow has not stopped.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.21,0:16:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it might keep snowing\Nthe rest of the year.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:31.13,0:16:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing planned.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:33.13,0:16:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be on your own?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:35.89,0:16:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.83,0:16:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't do!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.75,0:16:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot spend it alone!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.07,0:16:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nobody to spend it with.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:42.06,0:16:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't the three of you spend it together?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.99,0:16:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.99,0:16:46.01,Alt,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.01,0:16:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm up for it.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.33,0:16:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lonely spending New Year's by yourself.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:55.51,0:16:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:59.08,0:17:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, you should\Nhave a pajama party.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.10,0:17:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Paja— What?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:04.38,0:17:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls are beings that have pajama parties.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.43,0:17:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,At a recent conference, it was shown that
Dialogue: 5,0:17:10.91,0:17:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,more than an eighty percent have\Na pajama party by graduation.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.53,0:17:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What conference was that?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.63,0:17:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You will remain in the other twenty percent.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.29,0:17:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:23.03,0:17:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the daughter of the Nishikawa family!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.68,0:17:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I will execute a pajama party splendidly!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.48,0:17:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that sound good?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:30.83,0:17:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:31.58,0:17:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:33.24,0:17:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, just like our Christmas party the\Nother day, we will cook and have cake—
Dialogue: 5,0:17:37.33,0:17:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, pajama parties are a little different.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:40.31,0:17:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We just relax in bed talking\Nabout things in our pajamas.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:43.68,0:17:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.13,0:17:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a party?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.61,0:17:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have enough blankets\Nfor us at your place?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:53.43,0:17:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, er...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:32.18,0:18:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:35.43,0:18:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,People usually talk about\Npeople they like, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let us begin.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.18,0:18:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I love rice!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Paired with fried cod roe,\NI can eat it forever!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.03,0:18:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I love cats!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.73,0:18:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I love dogs too!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.83,0:18:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't decide between them!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:59.99,0:19:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Pajama... party...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:03.60,0:19:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot I made some snacks.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:06.22,0:19:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, then I will make some tea.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.38,0:19:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you oka—
Dialogue: 5,0:19:18.88,0:19:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is totally wrong{not a pajama party}.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:20.80,0:19:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A real pajama party has\Nmore squeals and giggles.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:27.50,0:19:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to do anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:34.53,0:19:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that camcorder for?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:37.13,0:19:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,To document the memories.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:41.53,0:19:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:42.78,0:19:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:44.38,0:19:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad that she will not spend\Nher New Year's alone, at least.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:24.82,0:20:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:27.23,0:20:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.83,0:20:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:30.83,0:20:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:34.53,0:20:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We got worked up and\Nfell asleep without realizing.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we did.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:44.16,0:20:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Food's almost ready.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:46.38,0:20:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:47.49,0:20:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:49.13,0:20:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:50.18,0:20:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We will eat soooooon....
Dialogue: 5,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's pound some mochi!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.63,0:20:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Pound mochi?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.63,0:20:55.73,Alt,,0,0,0,,Pound mochi?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:56.88,0:20:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:58.22,0:20:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:59.73,0:21:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a mochi pounding machine.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:10.58,0:21:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You said "pound mochi," so I thought\Nwe'd be using a mortar and pestle.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:15.18,0:21:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As did I...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:16.73,0:21:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked for it for my birthday!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:21.03,0:21:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:22.55,0:21:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat it now!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:25.28,0:21:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,After a pajama party,\Nthe high school girls eat mochi.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:29.28,0:21:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What a rare event.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:33.43,0:21:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have the\Ncamcorder out again?!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:34.48,0:21:35.48,Alt,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:41.38,0:21:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yummmmm!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:42.73,0:21:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so fresh...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:45.03,0:21:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is delicious.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:47.07,0:21:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:48.13,0:21:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Soy bean flour, spicy, pan-fried with soy sauce,\Nedamame paste, fermented soy bean, or walnut!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:53.39,0:21:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How many should we each have?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:54.83,0:21:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:55.53,0:21:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How many {\i1}each{\i0}?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:56.93,0:21:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mochi is a must-have on New Year's!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:00.03,0:22:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat as much as you want!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:01.93,0:22:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:02.69,0:22:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not competing in a big-eater contest!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:05.82,0:22:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:10.03,0:22:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, my name is Sonobe Shino.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:12.43,0:22:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Nishikawa Family's former maid.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:14.13,0:22:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The black-hearted class representative,\Nthe poor girl on a bread-crust diet,
Dialogue: 5,0:22:16.88,0:22:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and the walking black hole.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:18.43,0:22:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Their "to each their own color" life is so entertaining.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:21.69,0:22:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:23.03,0:22:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, listen to the "Rock Scissors Parade."
Dialogue: 5,0:22:25.33,0:22:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:00.78,0:01:02.43,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,You are wonderful, Miss Yoko.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:13.20,0:02:14.73,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.78,0:02:24.23,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko! Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.53,0:03:09.93,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:10.88,0:03:12.02,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Oh, Futaba.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:13.04,0:03:15.12,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Is Hayama at school already?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.99,0:03:33.26,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,{You}Miss Yoko will host the party,\NHayama will bring snacks, and...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.71,0:03:54.68,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,...Teru's...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.38,0:04:23.70,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Right, Miss Yoko?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:23.70,0:04:26.11,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Q-Quite right, Futaba!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.67,0:04:34.03,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Hayama's birthday is on Christmas.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:10.63,0:05:14.46,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko said she had\Nsomething to tell just me.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:17.33,0:05:19.52,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Wait, F-Futaba!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:31.78,0:05:35.27,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Let's throw a birthday party for Hayama,\Nbut pretend it's a Christmas party.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.10,0:05:54.85,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's keep it\Na secret from Hayama.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:42.28,0:06:43.88,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,You are wonderful, Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:19.13,0:07:20.58,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,H-Hayama!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:37.53,0:08:39.58,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} Hayama's birthday!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.28,0:08:43.60,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Nishiyama?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:49.78,0:08:52.78,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Hayama's birthday is on Christmas.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.91,0:10:24.83,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Oh, wait, Teru!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:31.08,0:10:34.09,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,I stewed it overnight for you, Teru!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.23,0:10:47.90,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Hayama's coming soon!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:52.33,0:10:53.28,Alt,sub 2,0,0,0,,Hayama!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.34,0:11:44.03,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Thanks, Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:02.53,0:12:04.38,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,M-Miss Yoko?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:07.88,0:12:08.93,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:20.83,0:12:22.18,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:56.63,0:12:57.78,Alt,sub 2,0,0,0,,Hayama...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.98,0:13:54.63,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,How can you make Miss Yoko shovel snow?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:55.83,0:13:58.18,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Sonobe, you must have made it snow!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.88,0:14:24.83,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Futaba!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.83,0:14:43.98,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Teru!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.93,0:15:42.93,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Teru?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.80,0:15:54.05,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Apparently Hayama got caught\Nin an avalanche in the garden!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:00.51,0:16:04.93,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Teru! Let's play!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.03,0:16:10.38,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Teru! Let's pla—
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.42,0:16:31.13,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko, what are you\Ndoing for New Year's?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.01,0:16:49.38,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,That is, of course, if Hayama\Nand Futaba agree to it.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:10.03,0:19:11.38,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Miss Yoko!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.28,0:19:27.50,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do, Sonobe?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.46,0:19:34.53,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,I just want Miss Yoko to experience\Nnormal high school girl things.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:22.43,0:20:24.82,Default,sub 2,0,0,0,,Good morning, Hayama.
